        "## **Geostatistics**  {.smaller}\n",
        "\n",
        "::: columns\n",
        ":::: column\n",
        "- **Data:** $(y_i, x_i)$, where $x_i \\in A \\subset \\mathbb{R}^2$  \n",
        "- **Model:** $Y_i = S(x_i) + Z_i$  \n",
        "- **Objective:** Estimate $\\int_{A} S(x) dx$ (e.g., mining yield)  \n",
        "::::\n",
        "\n",
